      "widgets_values": [
        "YouTube thumbnail design, cinematic photorealistic style with futuristic Art Deco design influence, ultra-clean composition, high contrast, realistic lighting and materials, high emotional intensity, not illustration, not poster art.\n\nVery dark background — deep navy blue to near-black gradient, subtle Art Deco geometric patterns barely visible in the background, thin symmetrical lines, matte metallic gold accents, minimal and elegant, no neon glow on UI elements.\n\nLEFT SIDE (TEXT ZONE)\n\nOn the left, huge bold matte white text with thin matte gold outline, all caps, stacked, ultra-readable, flat typography (no glow, no neon, no blur):\n\n\"QWEN IMAGE 2512\"\n\nText is clean, flat, razor-sharp, designed for maximum YouTube CTR.\n\nRIGHT SIDE (CHARACTER — MAX DYNAMICS)\n\nOn the right side, a hyper-realistic young woman archer, cinematic realism, dynamic mid-draw pose, realistic human proportions.\n\nLong dark hair, flowing freely, strong wind motion, individual strands visible\n\nHair partially crossing the face, creating dramatic depth\n\nLight-colored practical shirt (off-white / beige), realistic fabric folds\n\nAthletic but realistic build\n\nLatina or mixed-ethnicity appearance\n\nShe is pulling the bowstring back with visible muscle tension, shoulders engaged, body twisted in action, intense focused expression, fierce determined gaze aimed off-frame.\n\nHolding a modern composite bow, realistic materials (carbon, metal, matte finish), with subtle Art Deco geometry in the limbs and grip — restrained, elegant, functional.\n\nQuiver with arrows visible, clean silhouette.\n\nVISUAL EFFECT (ENERGY)\n\nFrom the drawn arrow and bowstring, controlled futuristic AI energy emerges — thin geometric light waves, directional particles, flowing forward with motion blur, softly glowing.\n\nGlow strictly limited to the energy only.\nColor palette: cyan, magenta, subtle gold accents — cinematic and restrained.\n\nBOTTOM ELEMENT\n\nAt the bottom of the frame, a wide matte UI-style banner, clean rectangular shape with slight rounded corners, physically realistic material.\n\nBold flat text inside:\n\n\"LORA + UPSCALE\"\n\nHigh contrast, no glow, no gradients, no blur.\n\nCOMPOSITION DETAILS\n\nStrong diagonal action line from arrow → text\n\nHair motion amplifies direction and energy flow\n\nCharacter fully on the right, text isolated on the left\n\nNo illustration feel, no poster vibe\n\nLooks like a high-end cinematic thumbnail\n\nBottom left corner: flat ComfyUI logo, minimal, no glow.\n\nResolution 1920x1080, aspect ratio 16:9, optimized for YouTube mobile CTR."
      ],
      "color": "#000000",
      "bgcolor": "#000000"
    },
